{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, this property is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two foci","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically, this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property has no effect if the "},{"code":"userTrackingMode","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value other than "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view with an animated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transition. If you don’t want to animate the change, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)targetCoordinate","title":"targetCoordinate","symbolKind":"property","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L752"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/targetCoordinate":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate","title":"targetCoordinate","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/